Package: crunchgeo
Type: Package
Title: Geospatial data on Crunch
Description: To facilitate visualizing and interacting with geospatial data on 
    the Crunch data platform <http://crunch.io/>, the 'crunchgeo' package 
    provides tools for working with geo- and topo-json files.
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2017-07-21
Authors@R: person("Jonathan", "Keane", role=c("aut", "cre"), email="jon@crunch.io")
Author: Jonathan Keane [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Jonathan Keane <jon@crunch.io>
URL: https://github.com/jonkeane/crunchgeo
BugReports: https://github.com/jonkeane/crunchgeo/issues
License: LGPL (>= 3)
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0),
    crunch,
    httr
